Produce final table of risk levels by epidemiological unit

risk_table.Rd

Represent the value of risk by epidemiological unit categorised into n risk-levels

risk_table(x, v, n)

Arguments

x

SpatialPolygons*. Epidemiological units.
v

Numeric. Risk values.
n

Number of risk levels.

Value

data.frame

Examples

  epi_units <- mapMCDA_datasets()$cmr_admin3
  risk <- runif(nrow(epi_units), 0, 100)
  risk_table(epi_units, risk, n = 4)
